lowercase-extension - Lowercase File Extensions

USAGE:
    lowercase-extension <file>

DESCRIPTION:
    Convert file extensions to lowercase. Supports JPG, CR2, and XCF
    extensions to ensure ease of use with shell scripts.

ARGUMENTS:
    file
        File to process (required)

EXAMPLES:
    lowercase-extension photo.JPG
    lowercase-extension image.CR2
    lowercase-extension design.XCF
